questions.quote: Did I tell you I ran into her last week? Ho-ho, she looked great.
Really John Mollika, they guy that used to bartend at the Comedy Club. How's he doing?
Never been a big fan. [coughing] Um..you know what? Has anyone ever told you you look exactly like Al Pacino? You know, " Scent Of A Woman." Who-ah! Who-ah!
Wait a second. Wait a second. You're right. I had both of them.
Let me ask you something. When's the last time you went skiing?
Oh, I had it perfectly timed out: the Grand Central, the Van Wyck! You destroyed my whole timing!
Excellent.  So, did you buy that electric toothbrush I was telling you about?
He wants to meet you? I'll tell you what. I'll show up. He doesn't know we're friends. I'll pretend I haven't seen you since High School. I'll back up the story.
Hi mom. So, what's happening with uncle Leo? Is he paying you?
What, do you think they just crack their knuckles and come out?
